report_guide.example: Total dollar sales of the selected product over the date range and across all selected stores. This is net of promotional discounts but does not reflect manufacturer coupons or rebates.

example.label: Sales $
example.name: sales_sales
example.report_guide: Total dollar sales of the selected product over the date range and across all selected stores. This is net of promotional discounts but does not reflect manufacturer coupons or rebates.

example.label: Units
example.name: sales_units
example.report_guide: Total unit sales of the selected product over the date range and across all selected stores. For random weight items each purchase is counted as one unit regardless of weight.

example.label: Cost $
example.name: sales_cost
example.report_guide: Total dollar cost of the selected products over the date range and across all selected stores.

example.label: Baskets
example.name: sales_baskets
example.report_guide: Number of baskets with at least one unit of the selected product over the date range and across all selected stores.

example.label: Stores Selling
example.name: sales_stores
example.report_guide: Number of stores with at least one unit sold of the product and store grouping corresponding to this row for the indicated date range. This is a measure of distribution, however it can be misleading for slow moving items if the date range is short or if the item may be on a special promotions in stores that do not normally stock it.

example.label: Extended PLU Price
example.name: sales_xpluprice
example.report_guide: Total dollar sales if the selected product were sold at PLU price for all transactions within the selected time frame and across all selected stores. PLU price represents the price ahead of discounts.

example.label: Weeks
example.name: sales_weeks
example.report_guide: Number of weeks included in the selected date range.

example.label: Units/Basket
example.name: sales_units_pt
example.report_guide: Average number of units of the selected product in a basket (among baskets with at least one unit of the selected product).

example.label: Sales $/Basket
example.name: sales_sales_pt
example.report_guide: Average dollars of the selected product in a basket (among baskets with at least one unit of the selected product).

example.label: Units/Store/Week
example.name: sales_units_psw
example.report_guide: Unit sales on a per store per week basis. This is calculated by taking the total unit sales for the item divided by (the number of stores X number of weeks). It includes promoted and non-promoted sales. This measure is often used as input to replenishment systems.

example.label: Sales/Store/Week
example.name: sales_sales_psw
example.report_guide: Sales $ on a per store per week basis. This is calculated by taking the total Sales $ for the item/(the number of stores x the number of weeks). It includes both promoted and non-promoted sales.

example.label: Baskets/Store
example.name: sales_baskets_ps
example.report_guide: Baskets on a per store basis. This is calculated by taking the total baskets for the item/the number of stores.

example.label: Avg Retail
example.name: sales_avgretail
example.report_guide: Average price per unit for the selected products in the date range. If product is a random weight item this is on a per purchase basis, not per unit of measure.

example.label: Avg. PLU Price
example.name: sales_avgplu
example.report_guide: Average price look up (includes regional zone pricing adjustments) across a given grouping level and time period. Item PLU detail is only available when grouping on the item level (i.e., sku)

example.label: Total Basket Sales $
example.name: sales_tot_basket_sales
example.report_guide: Total dollar sales of all baskets containing the given product over the date range and across all selected stores. This is net of promotional discounts but does not reflect manufacturer coupons or rebate.

example.label: % of Baskets
example.name: sales_pct_baskets
example.report_guide: Percent of the total number of baskets seen over the date range and across all selected stores.
